text: Chapayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnetroitsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 56 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Tuymazy, 8 km from Verkhnetroitskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Chapayevo, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
